{"tid":41762,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"吾女友搞到小巴司機專心唔到渣車","createTime":"2016-12-16T06:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T15:23:44.000Z","uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d420d5dfe7eca65c82657b3b42d5994e32f86f20","tid":41762,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:44:37.000Z","msg":"吾有一day由旺角返屋企，由於太夜，因此要搭亡命小巴<br />\n<br />\n在小巴上坐在司機後的一對情侶，在上車後不斷鬧交。<br />\n女的不斷鬧男是仆x，而男則鬧女的是死八婆。<br />\n經過15分鐘的「口部對戰」，男的終於忍不到，講了一句粗口。<br />\n<br />\n男︰「屄臭者，無法明也！」<br />\n女︰「若吾屄真臭，為何汝當舔？」<br />\n<br />\n突然全車靜晒，司機減速駕駛。<br />\n<br />\n各位男士要講粗口鬧人要三思<br />\n免得把生活公諸於世。"},{"pid":"fd54875af33d2660c5c3aa5b83b372cc0074e183","tid":41762,"uid":44584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:52:37.000Z","msg":"臭你又含<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b3820b394dfe61186fd6d917e61509e58da23f1","tid":41762,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:54:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b3182a607cedc9c0f8feffbfde89a128c7c6b81b","tid":41762,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:55:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc3f4d193ef21231f2451c34d284be5fb91f3ab0","tid":41762,"uid":57695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:56:41.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"9d139b642d5457e5cb8998087edc84bb8bafeb1f","tid":41762,"uid":57287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf801ba6eebea28ede5b41fab4ac2e52ba9ff26","tid":41762,"uid":31374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:58:36.000Z","msg":"read"},{"pid":"32d5cd037e30e166963b807a2a150898f11043d0","tid":41762,"uid":60339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T07:01:04.000Z","msg":"又撚狗<img src=\